    "10832390": {
      "title": "Consumption of fish products across the lifespan and prostate cancer risk",
      "abstract": "Objective: To examine whether fish and fish oil consumption across the lifespan is associated with a lower risk of prostate cancer.Design: The study was nested among 2268 men aged 67-96 years in th ..."
